            Ä‘á»ƒ gá»i Ä‘Ãºng <code>ITicketService.GetByEventAsync(eventId)</code>
            hoáº·c <code>_unitOfWork.Tickets</code> khi repository sáºµn sÃ ng.
            ViewModel: <code>TicketsByEventViewModel</code> Â· View: <code>~/Views/Ticket/TicketsByEvent.cshtml</code>
